Class InstanceDeclarationNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.TreeNode

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassNode, FieldNode, MethodNode

    public class InstanceDeclarationNode
extends VariableNode
    VariableNode extension that represents the declaration of a field or method. Contains the modifiers for visibility and whether or not the field/method is static.
    Since:
    v0.1 Jan 5, 2014 at 9:10:49 PM
    Version:
    v0.2.13 Jun 17, 2014 at 8:45:35 AM
